Film Journal International - December 2013  USA

132 Pages | True PDF | English | 24 MB 


Film Journal International, is a trade publication covering the motion picture industry, with special emphasis on theatrical exhibition. Articles report on U.S. and international news, with features on upcoming movies, industry trends, theatre design, equipment, concessions, digital cinema, sound, screen advertising, and other industry-related topics.
